{
  "stem": "26888.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't really-- at Munkatch, they didn't really-- did nothing for people who came home from the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't have where to go, we didn't have where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I met my husband, already, in [INAUDIBLE] that coat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somebody gave me an old coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was very big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and I was looking for a tailor to fix it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Didn't have a machine, didn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I went in, and there I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my husband remembers that-- it was across what kind of house we had there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met a man, his daughter was with me in Bergen-Belsen, but she didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked me-- he survived, the father survived-- I didn't tell him right away she didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on, he said he has a house there-- his own house, what he find, there was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was sleeping on the floors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can close the doors-- the knob was taken out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took out everything from that house-- even the knobs, couldn't close the door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were sleeping there on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was across the street, my husband was there, [? he saw-- ?] it was an awful thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then my sister got very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Still we came home, but she's better.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then she got very sick in that house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One night, she get convulsions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She got very sick, and I got very scared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they opened up, before a little bit, he opened up a kitchen for people, but not for staying-- like, you know, to sleep or something-- but that kitchen, it was a kosher kitchen, but they open up for people who came from the Holocaust, that they should have what to eat.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
